S.FORM: Don Betourne nalecuhan i Bourbonnais, Illinois, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. 2 bulad 27 demiad, 1915 a mihca, Don Betourne, miunduay. (mapatay i 2002 a mihca) namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
